To install simply edit the Makefile to point to your Lua and libpq installations:

-- # Lua setup
-- LUA= /usr/local
-- LUAINC= $(LUA)/include/lua51
-- LUALIB= $(LUA)/lib/lua51
-- LUABIN= $(LUA)/bin
--
-- # libpq setup
-- LPQ= /usr/local
-- LPQINC= $(LPQ)/include
-- LPQLIB= $(LPQ)/lib

The run 'make' and copy the pgsql.so/dll to somewhere in the Lua package.path (usually /usr/local/lib/lua/5.1)

Have fun!
